{"tid":1100693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"珠海海面現男浮屍 相信為划艇失蹤11日羅國勤","createTime":"2019-04-10T14:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T22:35:40.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"83da3c081575b141f42b22d152a1f981c1f91297","tid":1100693,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:35:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190410/59473346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59473346&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBToRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=dedc0baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190410%2F59473346&h=a2cf410a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190410/59473346</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">43歲羅國勤</span>在上月31日於大澳划獨木舟出海時失蹤，搜救隊伍事後在現場一帶海空搜索，但一直未有發現。事隔11日，香港警方接獲內地當局通知，指昨日（9日）有人於珠海對出海面發現一具男浮屍，相信為失蹤多日的羅國勤，正聯絡羅的家人了解事件。<br />\n失蹤的羅國勤，身高約1.75米，中等身材，黃皮膚及蓄短黑髮，最後露面時身穿藍和白色上衣及深色長褲。事發於3月31日，11名成人及1名小童分乘7艘獨木舟，由二澳向大澳方向前進，至傍晚6時許，其中一艘獨木舟在牙鷹角對開，疑抵受不住風浪反艇，獨木舟上的羅墮海失蹤，同伴搜尋無果；其餘6艘獨木舟返回石仔埗街大澳公眾碼頭後，友人報警，並留在碼頭等消息，警方及消防接報後出動船隻到事發水域搜救，政府飛行服務隊亦出動直升機在上空盤旋協助，可惜一直未有發現。"},{"pid":"a9054005fb84d190da0a96e8701ea8754644e4ea","tid":1100693,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:36:21.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5596e60c0a77c3baff6f7255f2a1219e3a52f5","tid":1100693,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"划艇冠軍<img src=